# 💱 Currency Convertor Web App

A simple and fast Flask-based web application to convert between different currencies.

---

## 🛠 Features

- 🌍 Convert between popular world currencies
- 🔥 Built with Python and Flask
- 🎨 Clean and simple UI with HTML templates
- 🧠 Accurate rates using predefined or live logic

